IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE FIFTEENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT, IN AND FOR PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA (CRIMINAL DIVISION)
TO: SUBPOENA COMPLIANCE
BellSouth Telephone Company
122 E. Lake Drive, Suite 300
Decatur, GA 30030
Fax Number: (404) 378-9269
DUCES TECUM: ANY AND ALL INCOMING AND OUTGOING PHONE CALLS FOR TELEPHONE NUMBER 561 FROM MARCH 1, 2006 TO PRESENT.
YOU MAY COMPLY WITH THIS SUBPOENA BY SUPPLYING THE INFORMATION TO DETECTIVE JOE RECARy, PALM BEACH POLICE DEPARTMENT, 345 SOUTH COUNTY ROAD, PALM BEACH, FLORIDA, FAX NUMBER (561) 655-9653, VOICE NUMBER (561) 838-5470.
GREETINGS:
You are hereby commanded to be and appear before a the State Attorney or his Assistant at the State Attorney's Office, 401 North Dixie Highway, West Palm Beach, Florida, on INSTANTER, 2006, for Interrogation and the truth to speak, In a certain matter pending and under investigation. Failure to appear will subject you to contempt of Court.
PLEASE DO NOT DISCLOSE THE EXISTENCE OF THIS REQUEST, AS IT MAY IMPEDE AN ONGOING CRIMINAL INVESTIGATION.
WITNESS my hand and the seal of this Court on the day of APRIL, 2006.
SHARON R. BOCK, Clerk
By: __________________________________ Deputy Clerk
(Circuit Court Seal)
FOR
DALIAH H. WEISS
Assistant State Attorney
Received this subpoena on the day of , 2006, and executed the same on the day of , 2006, by delivering a True Copy thereof to the within named witness in the County of Palm Beach, State of Florida.
SHERIFF, PALM BEACH COUNTY
By: __________________________________ Deputy Sheriff
07/26/17
Page 84 of 124
Public Records Request No.: 17-295
DOJ-OGR-00031805
